{"tid":1811160,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"朗尼曾沉迷賭博：影響場上表現","createTime":"2020-01-04T12:24:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-04T13:55:02.000Z","uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"28e787681f411f5caa8e978a1a037621e646254d","tid":1811160,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T12:24:01.000Z","msg":"【Now Sports-體育】剛為打比郡演出處子戰的朗尼自爆，曾經受賭博惡習影響表現，幸好現時已經走出困局。<br />\n<br />\n「當我年輕時，已經賺取很多錢。為曼聯、英格蘭出征要留在酒店7至10天，你會很苦悶，需要找些事情去打發時間，賭博就是其中一樣。」朗尼（Wayne Rooney）於一個控制賭博活動中表示。<br />\n<br />\n朗尼在場上贏多輸少，於賭局中初時也是這樣，但慢慢輸得愈來愈多，光透過電話便在5個月內賭輸70萬鎊，也曾於賭場只花2小時就輸了65000鎊：「我之後一直加注，希望把金錢贏回來。當你輸錢時，一定會影響代表球會及國家的表現。」<br />\n<br />\n這名34歲前曼聯、英格蘭代表隊隊長以過來人身份勸告大家：「幸好，我可以償還輸的錢，之後不再賭了，我從錯誤中學習。如果你繼續賭，只會輸得更多。」<br />\n<br />\n圖片來源 : Twitter圖片"},{"pid":"d7f12a1c14eeaf991d1a7cede35d5ccccdd93a4e","tid":1811160,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T12:26:03.000Z","msg":"佢一星期都30m磅啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d98da1f08f1f2328d8da3efc8192ba4c1981175e","tid":1811160,"uid":42246,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d7f12a1c14eeaf991d1a7cede35d5ccccdd93a4e","tid":1811160,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T12:26:03.000Z","msg":"佢一星期都30m磅啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T12:29:13.000Z","msg":"咪係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n5個月先輸70萬鎊<br />\n但一星期搵2x鎊<br />\n<br />\n條數咪同我地食飯錢差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a574f02f9ff878b89b4d10908e0b7ad33602081c","tid":1811160,"uid":48939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T12:29:36.000Z","msg":"屌佢講都有70萬 姐係最少要